"replaceable>,\n"
"                     int <replaceable>subRepeatInterval</replaceable>, \n"
"                     int <replaceable>subRepeatCount</replaceable>)"
msgstr ""
"bool scheduleMessage(const QString&amp; <replaceable>назва</replaceable>,\n"
"                     const QString&amp; <replaceable>повідомлення</"
"replaceable>,\n"
"                     const QString&amp; <replaceable>Дата_і_час_початку</"
"replaceable>,\n"
